N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 576.1 - Applicability of regulations

State Regulations

This Part shall govern vehicular traffic and parking upon
the streets and roads controlled or maintained by the State University Maritime

College, and shall apply to students, faculty, employees, visitors and all
other persons upon such premises. Notes
